45420d8f4119c222768f7477fafa4ffcbd479948f5b6d06f74726700b1645579fb6647f81247b0b281dcde0df010c7811c954021f2a477a88a40acd232247336  0001-fix-build-failure-due-to-typo-in-the-build-script.patch
"
